en_160420_0	A boyfriend who has uploaded his girlfriend’s naked photos on Facebook after breaking up with her culminating the affair of several years, has been remanded until the 12 th this Month.
en_160420_1	Negambo acting Magistrate, K.G.Gunadasa has issued this order.
en_160420_2	It is reported that the suspect is a 24 year-old resident in Thanamalwila who is employed in a private firm.
en_160420_3	He has revealed that he provided money for his girlfriend’s educational purposes as well as for her family matters.
en_160420_4	Later, with the girl entering into the University, she and her family has stopped connnections with this boy.
en_160420_5	The boy who was angered by this has edited his girlfriend’s photos as naked photos and has uploaded on Facebook.
en_160420_6	Moreover, he has included the girl’s and her mother’s contact numbers with the uploads.
en_160420_7	The investigations have been commenced by Ja-Ela police following a complaint made to the police by the girl and her mother.
